        {
            "id": 4116159604063021,
            "definition": {
                "type": "note",
                "content": "[Zscaler Internet Access](https://www.zscaler.com/products-and-solutions/zscaler-internet-access) (ZIA) is a secure Internet and web gateway delivered as a service from the cloud.\n\nThis dashboard provides a focused view of SaaS security activity monitored through Zscaler Internet Access, enabling visibility into user interactions, application usage, and potential risks across cloud-based services.\n\nFor more information, see the [Zscaler Integration Documentation](https://docs.datadoghq.com/integrations/z-scaler/).\n\n**Tips**\n- Use the timeframe selector in the upper-right corner of the dashboard to change the default timeframe.\n- Clone this dashboard to rearrange, modify, and add widgets and visualizations.",
